 THE lawmaker representing Ogun East Senatorial District, Senator Buruji Kashamu has denied moves to join the All Progressives Congress, APC. May 20, 2019 In "News" THE Senator representing Ogun East Senatorial District, Buruji Kashamu has vowed that the People’s Democratic Party, PDP, would wrest power from the ruling All Progressives Congress, APC, in Ogun State in the 2019 elections. April 10, 2018 In "News" THE People’s Democratic Party (PDP) in Ogun State is on the verge of becoming an empty house following the rift arising from its recent primaries on account of the emergence of some candidates believed to be loyal to Prince Buruji Kashamu. January 9, 2015 In "Politics"